when someone really loves

00:18:07.046 --> 00:18:07.676 A:middle
something.

00:18:08.436 --> 00:18:10.356 A:middle
And to Elaine's first point, you

00:18:10.356 --> 00:18:11.376 A:middle
know, I think everyone here

